ell with peace. Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/four-rakaat-before-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":4008,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sunan: Four raka&#8217;at of prayer before &#8216;Asr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray four cycles before afternoon prayer, separating them with the invocation of peace upon the favored angels and those who follow them among the Muslims and believers. Al-Tirmidhi said, \"Ibrahim ibn Ishaq preferred not to separate\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31757,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/03\/no-salat-asr-fajr-exceptions\/","url_meta":{"origin":4008,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: No voluntary prayer after \u2018Asr and Fajr, with exceptions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, only prayed two cycles after the afternoon prayer because some property came to him, which occupied him from performing two cycles after the noon prayer. The Prophet prayed them after the afternoon prayer and he did not repeat it.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17548,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/al-shafiee-wujud-creator\/","url_meta":{"origin":4008,"position":3},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Creation: Unity of creation proves existence of Creator","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Kathir reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked about the existence of the Creator, so he said, \u201cThe leaves of a berry bush all have one taste. Worms eat it and produce silk, bees eat it and produce honey. Goats, camels, and cows eat it and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/division-sahabah-surah-juz\/","url_meta":{"origin":4008,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: How companions divided the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aws ibn Hudhayfah reported: I asked the companions of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, how they divided the Quran. They said, \u201cThree chapters, then five, then seven, then nine, then eleven, then thirteen, and then al-Mufassal as a single part.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1393\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14036,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/07\/ibn-masud-quran-old-treasures\/","url_meta":{"origin":4008,"position":5},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Quran: Middle chapters are my old treasures","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Yazid reported: Ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said about Surat Bani Isra'il, Al-Kahf, Maryam, Ta Ha, and Al-Anbiya', \"They were among the first chapters I learned and they are my old treasures.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4431 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u064a\u0632\u064a\u062f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4008","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4008"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4008\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\